GUIDE TO EXTEND PAToS
=====================

1. Annotating new pedagogical (or for the matter linguistic) phenomena
----------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Get acquainted with the linguistic apparatus:
  a) Execute ProcessSPinTX.sh all
  b) Take a look at the files in $SPINTX_HOME/corpus/cg3. These files
  use the format and contain the information on which you can base your 
  annotation.
  c) Take a look at the VISL-CG3 documentation on the web to get used
  to CG3 file structure and rule syntax. See 
  http://www.divvun.no/doc/tools/docu-vislcg3.html

2. Make a copy of the file SpintxGrammar.rle in 
  $SPINTX_HOME/spintxPedagogicalAnntotation/grammars.

3. Start by creating a simple rule using for instance the operator ADD.


